description: Archives GuardDuty findings that are specified by the list of finding IDs.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The ID of the detector that specifies the GuardDuty service whose findings you want to archive. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: FindingIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the findings that you want to archive. (string) ---
